<org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription xmi:version="2.0" xmlns:xmi="http://www.omg.org/XMI" xmlns:org.eclipse.epf.uma="http://www.eclipse.org/epf/uma/1.0.6/uma.ecore" xmlns:epf="http://www.eclipse.org/epf" epf:version="1.5.1" xmlns:rmc="http://www.ibm.com/rmc" rmc:version="7.5.1" xmi:id="-xBlKMj_poFBpwaaNd5ZZ5A" name="plan_team_preparation,_tXztAHFeEdy8Ac588DXPCQ" guid="-xBlKMj_poFBpwaaNd5ZZ5A" changeDate="2008-01-11T11:13:53.562-0800" version="7.2.0">
  <sections xmi:id="_Xf460Hd6Edyqd9oUl_5ulw" name="Determine Test Team Skill Requirements" guid="_Xf460Hd6Edyqd9oUl_5ulw">
    <sectionDescription>Review the test strategies that will be employed to identify test team skills for a particular test effort. Ensure that the&#xD;
right mix of testing roles is achieved based on the test objectives in the Test Strategy.</sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <sections xmi:id="_bQ_08Hd6Edyqd9oUl_5ulw" name="Capture Test Team Preparation Requirements" guid="_bQ_08Hd6Edyqd9oUl_5ulw">
    <sectionDescription>By discussing the test effort with technical leads and product domain experts, determine specific test team preparation&#xD;
needs. Consider both managerial and technical skills for the given testing effort, and document the test roles and&#xD;
responsibilities in the test plan based on specific test team needs.</sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <sections xmi:id="_detCoHd6Edyqd9oUl_5ulw" name="Compile Comprehensive List of Test Team Preparation Objectives" guid="_detCoHd6Edyqd9oUl_5ulw">
    <sectionDescription>Based on the test roles and responsibilities captured in the test plan, develop a list of test team objectives for the&#xD;
given test effort. Include this information in the test plan.</sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <sections xmi:id="_jo1poHd6Edyqd9oUl_5ulw" name="Discuss Test Team Role and Responsibility Assignment with Test Staff" guid="_jo1poHd6Edyqd9oUl_5ulw">
    <sectionDescription>Clarify test role and responsibility assignment with test staff. Ensure that the given staff member understands the role(s)&#xD;
as well as the function of the role(s) within the test team.</sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <sections xmi:id="_qp9jAHd6Edyqd9oUl_5ulw" name="Review Test Team Preparation Plan" guid="_qp9jAHd6Edyqd9oUl_5ulw">
    <sectionDescription>Meet with technical leads and product domain experts to review the test team planning, and update the test plan to reflect&#xD;
the test team requirements and project staff assignment of test roles and responsibilities. If the test team is part of a&#xD;
larger &lt;i>roles and responsibilities&lt;/i> matrix for the project, provide this information to the project manager.</sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <purpose>&lt;p>&#xD;
    The purpose of this task is:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        To define the test team preparation objectives&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        To plan for the test team preparation content&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></purpose>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription>
